Awalam yaraw kayfa yubdio All<u>a</u>hu alkhalqa thumma yuAAeeduhu inna <u>tha</u>lika AAal<u>a</u> All<u>a</u>hi yaseer<b>un</b>
Qul seeroo fee alar<u>d</u>i fa<b>o</b>n<i><u>th</u></i>uroo kayfa badaa alkhalqa thumma All<u>a</u>hu yunshio a<b>l</b>nnashata al<u>a</u>khirata inna All<u>a</u>ha AAal<u>a</u> kulli shayin qadeer<b>un</b>
