Wam<u>a</u> antum bimuAAjizeena fee alar<u>d</u>i wal<u>a</u> fee a<b>l</b>ssam<u>a</u>i wam<u>a</u> lakum min dooni All<u>a</u>hi min waliyyin wal<u>a</u> na<u>s</u>eer<b>in</b>
