Fam<u>a</u> k<u>a</u>na jaw<u>a</u>ba qawmihi ill<u>a</u> an q<u>a</u>loo oqtuloohu aw <u>h</u>arriqoohu faanj<u>a</u>hu All<u>a</u>hu mina a<b>l</b>nn<u>a</u>ri inna fee <u>tha</u>lika la<u>a</u>y<u>a</u>tin liqawmin yuminoon<b>a</b>
Waq<u>a</u>la innam<u>a</u> ittakha<u>th</u>tum min dooni All<u>a</u>hi awth<u>a</u>nan mawaddata baynikum fee al<u>h</u>ay<u>a</u>ti a<b>l</b>dduny<u>a</u> thumma yawma alqiy<u>a</u>mati yakfuru baAA<u>d</u>ukum bibaAA<u>d</u>in wayalAAanu baAA<u>d</u>ukum baAA<u>d</u>an wamaw<u>a</u>kumu a<b>l</b>nn<u>a</u>ru wam<u>a</u> lakum min n<u>as</u>ireen<b>a</b>
Fa<u>a</u>mana lahu loo<u>t</u>un waq<u>a</u>la innee muh<u>a</u>jirun il<u>a</u> rabbee innahu huwa alAAazeezu al<u>h</u>akeem<b>u</b>
