Waloo<u>t</u>an i<u>th</u> q<u>a</u>la liqawmihi innakum latatoona alf<u>ah</u>ishata m<u>a</u> sabaqakum bih<u>a</u> min a<u>h</u>adin mina alAA<u>a</u>lameen<b>a</b>
